Welcome to BarMeUp! BarMeUp serves to show you which bars and clubs are nearby so you don't have to argue with your friends about where to go out until it's already too late to
go out and then the whole NIGHT IS RUINED MELISSA! IT WAS MY BIRTHDAY!
