Sorry about that. BarMeUp also has a handy API for developers that will give them access to the database in JSON format. Developers can simply call /api/clubs to grab a list of all the clubs, bars, and pubs in our database.
You can also request a list of different types of buildings, for example, /api/clubs/Bars for bars. You can also add a club using POST with /api/club. If you have any questions, please contact us through our <a href="support.php">support page</a>.
